::Feline::

She wondered if Skulletron would blow his cover.  She had her plans.  
She was out to exceed Zardus' expectations of her.  She knewe that 
she could gain great favor from Zardus if she played her cards 
right.  She had the plans, and Skulletron had them.  She planned to 
get the info from Skulletron.  She would have him come to her lab 
under the pretence of an upgrade or something.  Then put him into a 
deep sleep and get the ship's plans from his memory banks.  Then she 
would program the injured bots to do her bidding and cause chaos in 
the maximal base.  She smiled and started making the chips that would 
programs the bots to follow her orders.
